column5: So, I got the okay from my wife to start fishing again which is fantastic. I still have a bit of my gear - I think. I found all my rods, my waders and boots, hell even some of my old boxes of lures.... too bad I can't find my good reels lol....  On the positive note I get to go shopping!
WHOOT-WHOOT!! (PS stil have the band saw if still needed and or still looking)
